            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The index for <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> was prepared by <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1179.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">William Sweetland Dallas</ref> (see <hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi> vol. 15).</note>
